n.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-th%C3%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-khanh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-t1Bg9fnGVU0OR78wwl34cQ">Phụng tặng thái thường Trương khanh nhị thập vận - 奉贈太常張卿二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%E1%BB%A9-thi%E1%BA%BFt-2/poem-1Spbm-BMlvtOhgcIfGChbw">Tứ thiết 2 - 駟驖 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/V%C3%A2n-C%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B1-c%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng/poem-m1nOeI4mmRsvEvxtBCqZOw">Vân Cư tự cô đồng - 雲居寺孤桐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Jeongbeopsa/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-UMW9DDTMKnoIVmsNUmP-lg">Vịnh cô thạch - 詠孤石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Jeongbeopsa/author-a48yKgKc76edHWj4yWT4uQ">Jeongbeopsa</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
